# Coding Workshop

Repl.it is a tool that allows you to try out coding tricks without using a text editor.  You can display and edit
a block of code within the browser.

You can then run the code to see how it works


## Use on New Page

Visit the page to experiment with the code

* [Resulting Page](https://Box-Model--markseaman.repl.co)

* [Edit Code](https://repl.it/@MarkSeaman/Box-Model)


